Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:06.73,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Song: Mystery Eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.48,0:00:06.73,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Song by: Garnet Crow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:03.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is no shape to flowing water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blowing winds can't even be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.31,0:00:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what the case is, the deductions are free.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The super car, full of adoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:10.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not only expensive, but also\Ncausing complicated emotions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:12.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seeing through the one and only truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:14.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The appearance of a child but the intellect of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan.
