Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:47.00,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,A Super Car's Trap
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.24,0:01:47.00,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.83,0:01:44.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A Super Car's Trap (Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! It's so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can see the ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.67,0:01:53.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.38,0:01:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where's uncle?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird. He was walking with us just a moment ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.72,0:02:05.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Stop resting without me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Winning the 1st place in the city lottery was good,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.69,0:02:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But getting invited into a hotel where no bus line reaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:17.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.74,0:02:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a long way to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.66,0:02:24.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it was too good to be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.49,0:02:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The 2nd place with the all-you-can-eat\Nshabushabu would have been better, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're damn right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.50,0:02:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't ruin my good mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:38.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you say so... When will we arrive at the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be there soon, just hold out a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! I think that may be the Kirigamini-Hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.52,0:02:50.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please sign in on the registrating card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.73,0:02:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Mouri...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:55.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! It's Mr. Mouri, right? It'll be room 201.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:03.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey you! It's quite a nice hotel but,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.74,0:03:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can't you send out a bus to the\Nstation or do some service like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it already, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:14.84,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Suguro Hisashi (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:14.84,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Kirigamini Hotel Front Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:14.71,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I apologize, but I'll guide you to your room now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.21,0:03:17.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry. Let's go, Conan-ku...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.30,0:03:22.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}? Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.34,0:03:26.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahh! Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:34.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.27,0:03:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always wandering off like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look! It's so amazing! There\Nare so many historic sport cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:44.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.82,0:03:48.49,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Jaguar XK120
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:47.95,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Here is the Jaguar XK120.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The long stretched nose and this beautifully curved fender\Nare its characteristics. It looks like a real jaguar, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even nowadays, it's still the\Ndream of many Jaguar collectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:02.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:08.18,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Mercedes Benz 300SL Gullwing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:08.18,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This is the Mercedes Benz 300SL Gullwing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:11.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gullwing means the wings of a seagull.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:16.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The sight of the car when its doors are\Nopen is similar to the stretched seagull wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:18.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:22.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! Isn't that one over there called a Cadillac?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.57,0:04:27.37,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Cadillac Eldorado
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:26.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yes. Cadillac Eldorado a '53 Convertible.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:31.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's really powerful and was\Ncalled the ultimate American model.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The production was limited to 500 cars and\Ndisappeared from the showrooms in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:43.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, there is even an Eldorado\Nlegend told among the collectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:45.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know quite a bit, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.59,0:04:51.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This here is the newly built historic car exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This hotel's owner is quite a car maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:05:00.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just for this exhibition, he reconstructed the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? There's an open spot in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.07,0:05:10.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. That space is reserved for\Nthe owner's proud Ferrari Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:13.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? By Ferrari Dino...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mean the 206GT, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's exactly what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.79,0:05:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.30,0:05:24.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan? What kind of a car is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:30.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only 152 of them were ever produced, so\Nit's almost impossible to get one nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:36.35,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Ferrari Dino 206GT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:37.06,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Dino is the Ferrari's founder, Enzo\NFerrari's only son, Alfreadino's nickname.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.10,0:05:40.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He died at age 24.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the engine he developed\Nbefore his death was used in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:51.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why Enzo Ferrari chose his\Nbeloved son's name as the brand name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.41,0:05:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It had such a background to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Suguro!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:06:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you, whose job is at the front desk, doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.88,0:06:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And dear guests,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:09.64,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Kuroiwa Zenkichi (45)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:09.64,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Kirigamini Hotel Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:09.34,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This area is prohibited from entering,\Nuntil the opening ceremony tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.68,0:06:11.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.73,0:06:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guest... Could he be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.00,0:06:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chief, welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:45.30,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Teraizumi Daigo (60)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.87,0:06:45.30,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Kirigamini Hotel President
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:42.25,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,This car is more important than my life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:45.84,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Yet it is still exhausting to drive it all the way from Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:50.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chief, we have finished placing the other cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:52.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would suggest to place this car now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.26,0:06:55.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait! Don't be so hasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.10,0:06:58.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to spend tonight with him, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:04.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once he's on display, I won't be able to\Ndrive him anytime I want as I usually do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:07.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chief, I wanted to show you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.78,0:07:10.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Detective...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the hell? There's only one bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.33,0:07:19.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't act so spoiled. Be happy you even won the lottery.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't sleep in a room like this with three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's ask them to give us another room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.00,0:07:27.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay if we use the sofa.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Selfish old man as usual...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.13,0:07:32.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's okay, let me take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The opening ceremony will start tomorrow at 3 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So tonight is the last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll stick to our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.94,0:07:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you come here for a moment, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, that's enough, father!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.57,0:07:57.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This hotel is almost empty anyways!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely make them give us another room!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.83,0:08:04.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, won't they take more\Nmoney if we do something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:08.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if you are too loud and\Nannoying, they might kick you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:14.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Mouri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Threatening letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:22.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see... "Don't open the exhibition. You'll regret it."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This threatening letter was\Nsent to our hotel a few days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.48,0:08:30.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we were discussing what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.15,0:08:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For a threatening letter, it lacks impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably it's just a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:39.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.24,0:08:44.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But couldn't you guard me until\Nthe opening ceremony tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:49.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We would like to assign the\Nfamous detective Mouri Kogorou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:52.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you contact the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.34,0:09:01.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you accept, I will give you the\Npride of this hotel, this suite room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:05.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This suite room? Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand! I'll accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.98,0:09:16.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone, please just pretend that\Nyou're on a giant cruise and relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Miss Ran. How about a drive in my car after dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? She gets to go on the Dino? Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.43,0:09:44.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mister? I can also come, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.60,0:09:46.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, you may!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.81,0:09:49.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,May I also go, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.65,0:09:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah! This steak is really delicious! Great! Really delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold back a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is really good! One more plate!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.50,0:10:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Did it get on your clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:10.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem, I'll just go change right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Father! You're drinking too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.42,0:10:16.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Chief! It's terrible! The car displayed in the exhibition!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't stop me, Don't stop me please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.55,0:10:24.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please calm down, Mr. Ootake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.97,0:10:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:29.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get in my way! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please let me do what I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.56,0:10:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop acting foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'll turn this car into scraps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ootake, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.20,0:10:42.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasn't this car like a treasure to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.16,0:10:43.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.03,0:10:47.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? He was trying to destroy his own car?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.62,0:10:49.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ootake, you really are a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:53.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll never understand an emotion like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll... I'll crush this exhibition!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:18.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This car, '53 El Dorado Convertible was my dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:23.99,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Ootake Ichirou (55)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.44,0:11:23.99,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Travel Agency Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:25.03,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,In order to make that dream a reality, I worked\Nday and night and finally managed to get this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:29.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why did you want to destroy such an important vehicle?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I must give up this car, then I'd rather destroy it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:37.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you must give it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.00,0:11:39.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.67,0:11:41.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do I mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:45.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you ask Teraizumi there, you'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:48.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does this mean, Mr. Teraizumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:55.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a big misunderstanding. Mr.\NOotake, you should thank me, not hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:12:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be thankful!? Nobody is\Nlooking forward to this car exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Except you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:11.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly. I can understand why Mr.\NOotake would rather destroy his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:17.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's true that nobody's looking forward to this exhibition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:20.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but you guys are?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:26.01,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Sagara Shinsuke (37)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.42,0:12:26.01,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Car Repair Factory Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.55,0:12:26.68,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm Sagara Shinsuke, who was forced to\Ngive up this beloved just like Ootake{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:31.31,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Kameoka Jiyouji (40)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:31.31,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Car Realtor Company Manager
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:31.39,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm Kameoka Jiyouji, ex-owner of that Jaguar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All three of us here got our beloved car\Ncheated away by Teraizumi over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's your own fault that your car is taken, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by cheated?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We three have little firms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.29,0:12:51.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a travel agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.37,0:12:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a realtor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.62,0:12:56.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I have an auto bodyshop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:13:00.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But because of bad economy...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:07.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Teraizumi offered to lend us some\Nmoney if we put our cars as collateral.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We accepted, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.93,0:13:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that was a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.60,0:13:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We learned later, that man there\Nmanipulated from the back and took our businesses away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:25.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Finally, when we couldn't pay\Nback the loan, Teraizumi took our cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraizumi lent us the money with the intent of\Ntaking our cars away from us since the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.16,0:13:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.04,0:13:41.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any proof that I'm\Nthe reason for your business troubles?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you got the time to criticize me, I suggest\Nyou think of some ways to return the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.97,0:13:50.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you pay me back, I'll return the cars anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:51.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Threats won't work on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.27,0:13:59.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, you three sent me that threatening letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Threatening letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.65,0:14:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:08.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't lie. I will open this exhibition no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:14.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sagara's shoes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.25,0:14:18.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The opening is tomorrow at 3pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight is our last chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.05,0:14:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly! Don't worry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll stick to our plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:31.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sagara, what is your room number?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:42.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's 202.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there anything wrong with my room?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.03,0:14:48.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not really,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:54.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you could tell me things\Nabout your 300SL tonight because it's really cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.12,0:14:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't tonight. I have things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.62,0:15:01.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of things?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:04.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's none of your business, is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Room service? I didn't ask for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure this isn't some mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.64,0:15:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's on the hotel since you're the owner's guests.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please order anything you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:30.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! In that case, I'd like a nice bottle of wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:38.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry about stains on\Nyour pants earlier at the dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I changed immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.88,0:15:46.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dino's engine...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right, I hear a car's engine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:54.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Dino... There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.30,0:15:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:02.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Owner, where are you going at a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.06,0:16:07.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks to those guys, my good\Nmood is ruined... I'm going for a drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tonight's fog is thick so you should stay in, Mr. Teraizumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:16.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's safer on the road than in the hotel with those three.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:26.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please drive carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:28.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:53.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Manager, the owner still isn't back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.65,0:16:58.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geeze, it's nine already,\Nwhere in the world did the chief go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.70,0:17:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's still not back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What a hopeless guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.08,0:17:09.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the opening ceremony isn't till 3pm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:11.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still have enough time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.67,0:17:14.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't even a joke anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:16.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still have to exhibit Dino.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:20.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And in the afternoon, the\Nspecially invited guests will arrive as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:24.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, isn't it strange that he didn't contact us all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:27.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teraizumi is still not back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Kameoka and Ootake...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if he had an accident,\Ntoday's opening is cancelled, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's God's punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:41.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't the owner have a cell phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.54,0:17:44.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, I've totally forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.21,0:17:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let me talk to him and tell him to stop making us worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.21,0:17:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.92,0:17:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me Mouri, where are you right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:04.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where am I? Why is it so dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.23,0:18:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dark?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:10.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello? Owner? Owner?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.31,0:18:11.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.57,0:18:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, he seemed to be in pain and\Nmoaned, "Where am I? It's so dark,"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the line went dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dark? It's pure white outside with the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.99,0:18:25.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did he mean by dark then, Mouri{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:39.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sir, it's 10 am already. We\Nneed to prepare the ceremony soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right. Go ahead Suguro.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.72,0:18:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:51.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems that today's opening is cancelled, cancelled!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.19,0:18:53.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the God's punishment, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.73,0:18:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man... It's just as the threatening letter said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:00.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ahhhhhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.29,0:19:10.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:15.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:24.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}, what happened? Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.35,0:19:27.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:37.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I was taking a walk when somebody\Nsuddenly talked to me and I got scared in the fog and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the guardsman Noda. What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:49.00,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Noda Kazuo (50)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:49.00,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Guardsman
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:51.33,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Nothing, I warned that girl because\Nshe was walking toward the cliff in the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:54.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then she just started screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.42,0:19:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're such a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.46,0:20:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A car's coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.55,0:20:02.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the owner finally returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.43,0:20:07.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No no, that's not the owner, it's Mr. Sagara's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.98,0:20:18.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on, all gathered here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.94,0:20:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:24.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's amazing how you can tell whose\Ncar it is just by hearing the engine sound!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.91,0:20:28.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If it's a regular guest, then I know the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.83,0:20:31.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I still have work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.08,0:20:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Sagara, where were you last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.33,0:20:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was out for a drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you see the owner's car?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.42,0:20:47.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't. Now, step aside a\Nlittle, I'm going to park my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.68,0:20:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Man, it's too late to display Dino in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.61,0:21:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We first have to find out where the owner is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we don't find out then we can't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:08.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Teraizumi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.16,0:21:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something is wrong with Teraizumi in his car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Owner!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Teraizumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Owner!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:32.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A doctor, get an ambulance, quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's already too late, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.90,0:21:47.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The cause of death is Carbon Monoxide-intoxication.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:51.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Engine's still running and the car is full of fume.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.99,0:21:56.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The exhaust must have backtracked into the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.87,0:21:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This looks like an accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.21,0:22:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The window is slightly opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.88,0:22:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, why the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this really an accident?
